metadata.description:
Os moradores da ilha de Cotijuba tem prazer de participa da semana de museus com participação dos artesãos  que através do Eco Museu da Amazônia  que desde 205 tem feito um trabalho com os nativos gerando renda a traves de seus artesanatos e mantendo um trabalho com o roteiro de visitação e a sim o eco Museu  da  Amazônia  tem dado sustentabilidade  a cultura dos povos originários da ilha de Ccotijuba.
O vídeo foi produzido pela Sra Iracélia moradora da Ilha de Cotijuba, voluntária do Ecomuseu da Amazônia, no Roteiro Patrimonial de Visitação/Ilha de Cotijuba, e no Roteiro de Memória/Ilha de Caratateua. As duas ilhas estão localizadas na Região Metropolitana de Belém/PA. Contato/zap (91. 98408.7200).

metadata.description:
This financial war against conservatives, over free speech, it needs to end. Banks and even online payment companies, should be considered as a basic telephone service, essential and illegal to deny, even if an executive order is necessary to maintain law, order and basic rights for all. It should never be tolerated for any financial companies, whether banks or credit card companies like Visa, Master Card, or even online payment like Paypal, to deny essential basic services to conservatives, or their social medias like GAB, BitChute, UGEtube and others, where constitutionally guaranteed free speech rights are still allowed, and attempting to financially pressure and try to starve their businesses, owners and even their family members, when not attacking conservative journalists, just because economic terrorists like George Soros buys shares of those financial companies to harass conservatives, or communist China having an interest as well. Economic terrorism of all forms should be stopped, and all financial companies should be forced by law to provide basic minimum services to all, or their top administration should be arrested and sent to jail, for as long as necessary, for them to understand, that trying to starve anyone, because you disagree with their political views, and refusing to respect the constitutional rights of every customers, is highly criminal. Trying to economically sabotage or starve your political opposition, should not only be illegal, it should be considered as economic terrorism, with very stiff jail sentences, at the very least.
